{"tid":1776656,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［真係咁講］鄧炳強：黨會繼續支持警隊止暴制亂！","createTime":"2019-12-09T16:28:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-09T16:34:51.000Z","uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"3e9d94ea8d1058385033aae9501d4a6c946f84b2","tid":1776656,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T16:28:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />由以前中央政府支持，國務院支持變到今日直接由黨支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n鄧炳強：黨會繼續支持警隊止暴制亂<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1496497-20191207.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1496497-20191207.htm&d=qnVsOlgekcepRBzFpIlw%2Fw6WLWD%2BvnO7xCw116w%2BR6c%3D&h=02510677\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1496497-20191207.htm&h=ebcaecb3\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1496497-20191207.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n在北京，警務處處長鄧炳強分別禮節性拜訪中共中央政法委書記郭聲琨、公安部部長趙克志及港澳辦主任張曉明。<br />\n<br />\n鄧炳強會見記者時表示，3人肯定警方過去6個月的工作，他又説，黨會繼續支持警隊止暴制亂。鄧炳強向3人介紹警方新的管理團隊、香港治安情況，以及討論雙方的警務協作。<br />\n<br />\n鄧炳強早上觀看升旗禮後，引述警方的新座右銘「忠誠勇毅」，希望警隊盡快投入止暴制亂。被問到是否包括對黨忠誠，他表示，忠誠是對香港市民、政府以及警隊堅守維護香港治安的信念。<br />\n<br />\n另外，鄧炳強說，贊成特首提出的獨立檢討委員會，檢視香港事態的背後社會成因，但如果成立獨立調查委員會，目的只是針對警方，並且打擊警方的調查和執法能力，並不公義，他不會同意，重申有關警方的行動，應該交給監警會調查。"},{"pid":"742b015cbc5b796d245db499d5335ea031747b97","tid":1776656,"uid":127553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T16:28:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UmKV2z6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUmKV2z6.jpg&h=241aee25&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有班教育界痴線佬為左唔比學生落入聖誕節圈套<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1776399\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1776399</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"62ccf5bb08029918afe2b242399bc6dcf3ca1500","tid":1776656,"uid":92908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T16:29:06.000Z","msg":"支那豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ad4ceecc62e777d506f5637f92dbeac7da28eaa","tid":1776656,"uid":177552,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T16:31:02.000Z","msg":"問左共和黨同民主黨未？"},{"pid":"105a79f73d79dd6f5f06204ea287af4385a364e9","tid":1776656,"uid":90601,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T16:32:27.000Z","msg":"小強爭在未讀埋施政報告 唔係已經取代特首 党性直逼當年689"},{"pid":"2138f18f92f588fcd95e67096a6ae2cc09fa3bf6","tid":1776656,"uid":259329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T16:33:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"778006490b30a9f954d0b879cb933b748bcd7385","tid":1776656,"uid":9315,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T16:34:24.000Z","msg":"外國人應該唔知頭唔知到<br />\n但如果識嘢嘅應該會發現香港大限差唔多到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今日嘅香港已經唔係9/6之前嘅香港  已經返唔到去<br />\n(除非共產黨被推翻/港獨)"},{"pid":"50655430fd8c8a79e3bc795006014facd3037134","tid":1776656,"uid":9315,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T16:34:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>外國人應該唔知頭唔知<span style=\"color: red;\">路</span><br />\n但如果識嘢嘅應該會發現香港大限差唔多到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今日嘅香港已經唔係9/6之前嘅香港  已經返唔到去<br />\n(除非共產黨被推翻/港獨)</blockquote>"}]}